msgid "Retry behavior:"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/WebhooksAdminPage.php:152
msgid "A non-2xx response (or a network failure) schedules a retry with exponential backoff (1m → 5m → 30m). After 3 failed attempts the webhook is automatically paused. Resume by editing the row in the database (set is_active=1) - admin UI flag in v1.1."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/WebhooksAdminPage.php:155
msgid "Payload shape:"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/WebhooksAdminPage.php:156
